<p class="doc">
    Installing Linux, especially these days is about as easy as installing windows or Mac OS X.  When you download and install any of the available Distro's they will come with an installation wizard to help guide you.  But let's say you wanted to go a bit deeper in understanding what exactly Linux is doing to your computer.  There are a few ways to do that.
</p>

